                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A shantak\u2019s scales seep slippery slime. This grants the creature a +8 bonus on all Escape Artist checks and to its CMD against grapples, and imparts a \u20135 penalty on all Ride checks made by creatures attempting to ride a shantak."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Starflight",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A shantak can survive in the void of outer space. It flies through space at an incredible speed. Although exact travel times vary, a trip within a single solar system should take 3d20 hours, while a trip beyond should take 3d20 days (or more, at the GM\u2019s discretion)\u2014provided the shantak knows the way to its destination."
